WEBVTT

00:00:02.129 --> 00:00:18.809
love? Is it gone? Have we lost it? Is it the possession of the wealthy, the strong,

00:00:18.809 --> 00:00:27.489
or is it somewhere else? At the 2019 Convention of Jehovah's Witnesses, you will learn what

00:00:27.489 --> 00:00:40.710
real love is, where to find it, how to show it, and have it shown in return. God cares deeply

00:00:40.710 --> 00:00:49.469
about you. And he wants you to know that in this hate-filled world, love can be found. It

00:00:49.469 --> 00:00:55.549
is not lost, and that love will never fail.
